QuestData.Title: Zao'cho the Wicked
QuestData.Description: Electricity hums in the distance, tickling your ears and sending impulses down your spine. Your fingers go numb, and your heart races as you approach the door ahead.$b$bZao'cho stands arrogantly atop the steps ahead, weaving lightning between his fingers and smirking at you with demented glee.
QuestData.PortraitGiverText: Looking directly into the lightning in Zao'cho's eyes is painful.
